<\/li><li>7\/24 sistem monitoring<\/li><li>Siber g\u00fcvenlik \u00f6nlemleri<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>11. ALTERNAT\u0130F UYU\u015eMAZLIK \u00c7\u00d6Z\u00dcM\u00dc<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>11.1 Arabuluculuk<\/strong><\/p><p>Uyu\u015fmazl\u0131k halinde \u00f6ncelikle arabuluculuk tercih edilir:<\/p><ul><li><strong>\u0130stanbul Arabuluculuk Merkezi<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Ticaret Odas\u0131 Arabuluculuk<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Online Arabuluculuk Platformlar\u0131<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>11.2 Hakem Kurulu<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Ba\u015fvuru Ko\u015fullar\u0131:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Parasal s\u0131n\u0131rlar dahilinde uyu\u015fmazl\u0131k<\/li><li>T\u00fcketici i\u015flemi olmas\u0131 \u015fart\u0131<\/li><li>\u0130\u00e7 ba\u015fvuru yollar\u0131n\u0131n t\u00fckenmesi<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Ba\u015fvuru Yerleri:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>\u0130l\/\u0130l\u00e7e T\u00fcketici Hakemlik Kurullar\u0131<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Online ba\u015fvuru:<\/strong> www.tuketici.gov.tr<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>12. MEVZUAT VE ATIF YAPILAN KANUNLAR<\/strong><\/p><p>Bu politika a\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki mevzuat \u00e7er\u00e7evesinde haz\u0131rlanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r:<\/p><p><strong>6502 say\u0131l\u0131 TKHK:<\/strong> T\u00fcketici haklar\u0131 ve cayma hakk\u0131<br \/><strong>6098 say\u0131l\u0131 TBK:<\/strong> S\u00f6zle\u015fme hukuku genel kurallar\u0131<br \/><strong>6563 say\u0131l\u0131 ETK:<\/strong> Elektronik ticaret \u00f6zel d\u00fczenlemeleri<br \/><strong>5464 say\u0131l\u0131 Banka Kartlar\u0131 Kanunu:<\/strong> \u00d6deme sistemleri<br \/><strong>6698 say\u0131l\u0131 KVKK:<\/strong> Ki\u015fisel veri koruma<\/p><p><strong>\u0130lgili Y\u00f6netmelikler:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Mesafeli S\u00f6zle\u015fmeler Y\u00f6netmeli\u011fi<\/li><li>Elektronik Ticaret Bilgi Sistemi Y\u00f6netmeli\u011fi<\/li><li>T\u00fcketici Hakemlik Kurullar\u0131 Y\u00f6netmeli\u011fi<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>13. POL\u0130T\u0130KA G\u00dcNCELLEMELER\u0130<\/strong><\/p>